<HEADLINE>
<P>
QUAKE FIX 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Feb. 1 story of the clock that started ticking after the recent earthquake 
struck home.I have a chime clock hanging on my office wall that had not been 
working for over two years. I thought of discarding it on many occasions but 
never got around to it. Lo and behold on the day of the quake I arrived in my 
office and the damned thing was ticking away and chiming! My office is in a 
hospital built like a fortress, but somehow the earthquake managed to revive 
this dormant timepiece. 
</P>
<P>
 C. C. CALESCIBETTA MD 
</P>
<P>
 Long Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
