FAVORITE PLACES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I enjoyed reading your new feature, Jane Spiller's "Favorite Places," in 
Voices, Jan. 24.The concept is refreshing and entertaining, particularly with 
the rebuilding challenges we all will be facing in the months ahead. 
</P>
