<TEXT>
<P>
 Security Environmental Systems Inc., which manages and disposes of hazardous 
waste, said its common shares will begin trading today on the Nasdaq market. 
</P>
<P>
 The Huntington Beach company's stock formerly traded on Nasdaq's "small-cap" 
listing. The company will keep SENV as its trading symbol. 
