<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * John M. DeStefanis has been appointed president and chief operating officer 
of Quantum Health Resources Inc., an Orange health care company. In those 
positions he succeeds Douglas H. Stickney, who will continue as chairman and 
chief executive. DeStefanis was formerly president and chief operating officer 
of Norrell Health Care Inc. in Atlanta. Before that, he held senior management 
positions with Caremark in Chicago, Foster Medical in California and USV 
Laboratories in Tarrytown, N.Y. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
