<TEXT>
<P>
 Randolph Childress scored 22 points in the second half and Wake Forest spoiled 
Duke's shot at the No. 1 ranking Sunday with a 78-69 upset of the second-ranked 
Blue Devils in an Atlantic Coast Conference game at Winston-Salem, N.C. 
</P>
