on Saturday at Chapel Hill, N.C. 
</P>
<P>
 On Jan. 13, with Duke ready to climb over the Tar Heels for No. 1, Childress 
made a three-point basket to give the Demon Deacons a 69-68 victory.This time, 
Childress did the bulk of his damage from the free-throw line. He made nine of 
10 free throws in the last 3:20. 
